ping%20its%20local%20edge%20as%20rivals%20flock%20to%20Paris%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226007%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20board%20of%20Capital%20Fund%20Management%20sits%20on%20a%20rooftop%20patio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6839a0236ffb6822ec61c763%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20board%20of%20CFM%2C%20from%20left%20to%20right%3A%20Jacques%20Sauli%C3%A8re%2C%20Marc%20Potters%2C%20Jean-Philippe%20Bouchaud%2C%20Philippe%20Jordan%2C%20and%20Laurent%20Laloux%3Cp%3ECapital%20Fund%20Management%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECapital%20Fund%20Management%20is%20a%20long-running%2C%20Paris-based%20quant%20investment%20firm.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20manager%20has%20maintained%20long-standing%20ties%20to%20top%20French%20schools%20even%20as%20it%20has%20expanded%20globally.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20%2418%20billion%20firm%20recently%20added%20NYU%20mathematician%20Eric%20Vanden-Eijden%20to%20lead%20an%20AI%20effort.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20ritzy%207th%20arrondissement%20of%20Paris%2C%20in%20a%20building%20that%20also%20counts%20fashion%20house%20Yves%20Saint%20Laurent%20as%20a%20tenant%2C%20%2418%20billion%20Capital%20Fund%20Management%20is%20hoping%20to%20straddle%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20quant%20firm%20is%20trying%20to%20retain%20what%20it%20believes%20is%20its%20edge%20%E2%80%94%20an%20academic%20culture%20with%20a%20French%20flair%20%E2%80%94%20while%20also%20expanding%20its%20reach%20and%20brand%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20manager%20is%20happy%20to%20see%20Paris's%20financial%20services%20footprint%20grow%2C%20but%20wary%20of%20new%20competition%20entering%20its%20backyard.%20CFM%20is%20simultaneously%20proud%20of%20its%2034-year-old%20history%20and%20constantly%20iterating%20on%20things%20that%20have%20historically%20been%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20apocalypse%20is%20on%20the%20horizon%20at%20all%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Philippe%20Jordan%2C%20the%20firm's%20president%2C%20from%20CFM's%20offices%20located%20on%20the%20River%20Seine's%20left%20bank%20across%20the%20water%20from%20the%20Louvre.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Jordan%20was%20being%20somewhat%20tongue-in-cheek%2C%20the%20constant%20anxiety%20is%20understandable%20in%20an%20industry%20hyper-focused%20on%20the%20what-you-have-done-for-me-lately.%20The%20firm's%20%2412.5%20billion%20flagship%20fund%2C%20Stratus%2C%20was%20up%2014.2%25%20in%202024%20and%20notched%20a%202.9%25%20return%20through%202025's%20first%20four%20months%2C%20despite%20losing%20money%20in%20April.%20The%20manager's%20longest-running%20fund%2C%20%242.2%20billion%20Discus%2C%20made%20more%20than%2010%25%20a%20year%20on%20average%20between%201991%20and%202024%2C%20but%20is%20slightly%20down%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm's%20academic%20and%20research-driven%20DNA%20is%20maintained%20by%20its%20ties%20to%20Paris's%20academic%20scene%2C%20which%20is%20known%20for%20mathematical%20talent%20from%20neighbouring%20universities%20like%20%C3%89cole%20Normale%20Sup%C3%A9rieure%20and%20%C3%89cole%20Polytechnique.%20It's%20something%20that%20the%20firm's%20hoping%20to%20hold%20onto%20despite%20fellow%20quant%20Qube%20Research%20%26amp%3B%20Technologies%20and%20giants%20like%20Point72%20establishing%20larger%20footprints%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm's%20office%20is%20a%20clean%20metaphor%20for%20how%20it%20is%20blending%20tradition%20and%20innovation%3A%20On%20a%20centuries-old%20street%20where%20Napoleon's%20chief%20diplomat%20and%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Three%20Musketeers%26quot%3B%20once%20lived%2C%20the%20glass%20conference%20room%20walls%20are%20filled%20with%20mathematical%20equations%20written%20in%20dry-erase%20markers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20constant%20race%20between%20alpha%20creation%20and%20alpha%20degradation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jean-Philippe%20Bouchaud%2C%20the%20firm's%20chief%20scientist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dc406385-2d33-4b7c-87bb-18d84177ed10%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAcademic%20inspiration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20dream%20of%20the%20manager's%20late%20cofounder%2C%20Jean-Pierre%20Aguilar%2C%20who%20died%20in%20a%20gliding%20accident%20in%202009%2C%20was%20that%20the%20firm%20would%20one%20day%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20cupboard%20full%20of%20computers%26quot%3B%20that%20just%20needed%20someone%20to%20turn%20it%20on%20to%20%26quot%3Bmagically%20make%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Laurent%20Laloux%2C%20CFM's%20chief%20product%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20of%20having%20technology%20and%20research%20interacting%20with%20capital%20markets%20to%20make%20money%20was%20there%20at%20day%20one%2C%20and%20we're%20trying%20to%20do%20it%2C%20but%20we%20have%20to%20evolve%20with%20the%20times%20in%20order%20to%20make%20it%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Laloux%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20research%20and%20technology%20side%2C%20it's%20making%20sure%20they're%20always%20on%20top%20of%20the%20latest%20discovery%20from%20academics%20and%20scaling%20internal%20computing%20power%20as%20fast%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20manager's%20latest%20big%20hire%20is%20NYU%20mathematician%20Eric%20Vanden-Eijden%2C%20who%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20cited%20researchers%20in%20his%20field%2C%20according%20to%20Google%20Scholar.%20He%20is%20leading%20an%20internal%20AI%20effort%20that%20will%20both%20publish%20academic%20papers%20and%20work%20with%20the%20firm's%20researchers%20to%20find%20new%20investment%20opportunities.%20The%20addition%20of%20Vanden-Eijden%2C%20the%20firm's%20executives%20said%2C%20came%20with%20the%20promise%20that%20any%20needed%20technological%20juice%20would%20be%20available%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ariel%20picture%20of%20Paris%20with%20Eiffel%20tower%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d06d53585f1dff88b1c926%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224071%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAsset%20managers%20are%20flocking%20to%20the%20City%20of%20Lights.%3Cp%3Esamael334%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EVanden-Eijden%20has%20known%20CFM's%20leadership%2C%20specifically%20Bouchaud%2C%20for%20years%20and%20was%20convinced%20to%20move%20from%20New%20York%20to%20Paris%20for%20the%20job.%20He's%20far%20from%20the%20only%20academic%20to%20be%20drawn%20to%20the%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20strives%20to%20hire%2015%20doctorates%20a%20year%20to%20its%20research%20team%2C%20and%20Bouchaud%2C%20who%20is%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20elite%20ENS%20where%20he%20got%20his%20doctorate%20in%20theoretical%20physics%2C%20said%20the%20firm's%20%26quot%3Boriginality%26quot%3B%20has%20come%20from%20CFM%20existing%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bborder%26quot%3B%20between%20finance%20and%20academia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20able%20to%20source%20inspiration%20from%20cutting-edge%20research%20of%20academia%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bouchaud.%20He%2C%20Laloux%2C%20and%20CFM's%20chief%20investment%20officer%20Marc%20Potters%20all%20have%20Ph.D.%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%20know%20that%20there's%20academic%20excellence%20in%20Paris%2C%20and%20there's%20quality%20of%20life%20in%20Paris%2C%20and%20so%20Paris%20is%20very%20attractive%20for%20people%20who%20we%20want%20to%20hire%2C%26quot%3B%20Bouchaud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20more%20competition%20than%20ever%20for%20this%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b9d63d4-623e-49e7-905c-96ed4176c83b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EParis%20push%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20capital%20has%20a%20long%20tradition%20of%20mathematical%20excellence.%20Its%20universities%20emphasize%20theoretical%20training%20and%20are%20top%20destinations%20for%20research.%20They%20have%20also%20produced%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20top%20math%20geniuses.%20Of%20the%2064%20winners%20of%20the%20Fields%20Medal%2C%20dubbed%20the%20Nobel%20Prize%20of%20math%2C%2013%20have%20been%20French.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20made%20it%20a%20hotbed%20of%20quant%20talent.%20Previously%2C%20top%20banks%20and%20asset%20managers%20would%20recruit%20graduates%20to%20join%20teams%20in%20New%20York%20or%20London.%20Now%2C%20many%20of%20these%20firms%20are%20expanding%20their%20presence%20in%20Paris%20to%20tap%20into%20this%20talent%20pool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFast-growing%20Qube%20is%20run%20by%20a%20group%20of%20former%20Credit%20Suisse%20traders%2C%20several%20of%20whom%20are%20French%2C%20from%20its%20London%20headquarters%2C%20but%20with%20an%20expanding%20Paris%20presence%2C%20as%20evidenced%20by%20the%20dozens%20of%20open%20roles%20in%20the%20French%20capital%20on%20its%20website.%20Quants%20like%20Squarepoint%20and%20Point72's%20Cubist%20unit%20have%20significant%20Paris%20headcounts.%20Quant-heavy%20multistrategy%20fund%20Centiva%20Capital%20opened%20up%20an%20office%20in%20the%20city%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Eisler%20partner%20Adrien%20Delattre's%20new%20firm%2C%20which%20will%20manage%20money%20exclusively%20for%20Millennium%20to%20start%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20industry's%20most%20closely%20watched%20launches%20and%20will%20operate%20out%20of%20Paris.%20RBC's%20BlueBay%20fixed-income%20investing%20unit%20is%20opening%20a%20Paris%20office%2C%20according%20to%20local%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20new%20firms%20here%20that%20poach%20from%20us.%20We've%20gone%20from%20being%20slightly%20provincial%20to%20being%20more%20plugged%20into%20the%20whole%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jordan%2C%20CFM's%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Bloomberg%20reports%20that%20some%20global%20investment%20banks%20may%20be%20slowing%20down%20their%20French%20expansion%2C%20given%20a%20tax%20increase%20and%20shaky%20domestic%20politics%2C%20buy-side%20firms%20continue%20to%20build%20out%20in%20the%20region.%20Data%20from%20regulatory%20filings%20compiled%20by%20fund%20tracker%20Old%20Well%20Labs%20show%20that%20Qube's%20investment%20staff%20in%20the%20city%20is%20now%20160%2C%20compared%20with%2050%20in%202022%2C%20while%20Point72%20and%20Citadel%20have%20more%20than%20doubled%20their%20Parisian%20trading%20staffs%20since%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20new%20competition%20for%20their%20talent%2C%20there's%20also%20a%20bigger%20overall%20pool%20of%20talent%20to%20fish%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20cited%20the%20firm's%20chief%20technology%20officer%2C%20Benjamin%20Roy%2C%20who%20most%20recently%20worked%20for%20French%20investment%20bank%20Societe%20Generale%20in%20New%20York%2C%20as%20someone%20whom%20the%20firm%20was%20able%20to%20recruit%20because%20the%20city's%20%26quot%3Becosystem%20is%20sufficiently%20large%20and%20healthy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20CFM's%20remains%20committed%20to%20its%20culture%20and%20Parisian%20roots%2C%20Jordan%20recognizes%20that%20there%20is%20no%20time%20for%20%26quot%3Bnostalgia%26quot%3B%20in%20asset%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm's%20foundation%20is%20just%20as%20important%20as%20its%20constant%20evolution%2C%20including%20its%20focus%20on%20growing%20globally.%20CFM%20has%20been%20building%20deeper%20relationships%20with%20distribution%20partners%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcfm-expands-america-plans-hires-parternships-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplaces%20like%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20financial%20advisory%20firm%20Stifel%2C%20which%20has%20several%20CFM%20funds%20on%20its%20advisors'%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20cares%20what%20you've%20done%2C%20they%20care%20about%20what%20you%20can%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Jordan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20survive%20and%20be%20successful%2C%20look%20at%20the%20future.%20Life%20is%20lived%20forwards%2C%20not%20backwards.%26quot%3B%3C%