0now%20built%20more%20than%20750%2C000%20mobile%20robots%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20its%20robotic%20arms%20and%20sortation%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EErica%20McClosky%2C%20director%20of%20manufacturing%20and%20technical%20operations%20at%20Amazon%20Robotics%2C%20leads%20teams%20that%20build%20and%20test%20robots%20before%20they%20are%20sent%20to%20fulfillment%20centers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Erica%20McClosky%20leads%20manufacturing%20for%20Amazon%20Robotics%20and%20is%20pictured%20wearing%20a%20pink%20sweater%20in%20front%20of%20Amazon's%20blue%20and%20green%20robots%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f69e6ca50259add4cd081%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMadeline%20Stone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20300%20people%20work%20on%20the%20physical%20side%20of%20building%20and%20maintaining%20Amazon's%20robotic%20fleet.%20The%20majority%20of%20those%20employees%20are%20on%20the%20assembly%20line%2C%20while%20others%20receive%20and%20ship%20materials%20and%20test%20and%20repair%20robots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20a%20very%20controlled%2C%20stable%20environment%20here%2C%20so%20we're%20able%20to%2C%20for%20all%20of%20our%20new%20products%2C%20continuously%20look%20at%20how%20we%20optimize%20the%20entire%20flow%2C%26quot%3B%20McClosky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHere%2C%20workers%20put%20together%20subassemblies%20that%20will%20be%20incorporated%20into%20Proteus'%20design.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20worker%20inside%20Amazon%20Robotics%20facility%20in%20North%20Reading%20assembles%20sub%20parts%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682f7d86ca50259add4cd4a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMadeline%20Stone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20manufacturing%2