0Floyd%20Mayweather%3Cp%3ELucy%20Nicholson%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20told%20BI%20that%20consumers%20have%20been%20pinched%20by%20inflation%20and%20have%20migrated%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgyms-outdated-cardio-no-squat-racks-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebigger%20box%20gyms%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20lower%20monthly%20membership%20rates%20and%20a%20menu%20of%20workout%20options.%20Technology%20has%20also%20allowed%20more%20gymgoers%20to%20work%20out%20at%20home.%20Those%20shifts%20have%20hurt%20higher-priced%2C%20niche%20studio%20concepts%20like%20Mayweather%20Boxing%20and%20Fitness%2C%20where%20a%20monthly%20membership%20at%20some%20locations%20can%20cost%20as%20much%20as%20%24300.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraditional%20gym%20memberships%20in%20the%20US%20have%20surpassed%20pre-pandemic%20levels%2C%20according%20to%20a%202024%20study%20from%20the%20Health%20and%20Fitness%20Association%2C%20an%20industry%20trade%20group.%20Boutique%20studio%20memberships%20remain%20below%20their%202019%20peak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20customers%20have%20found%20it's%20kind%20of%20easier%20to%20step%20away%20from%20those%20more%20niche%20studio%20memberships%2C%20as%20they%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20view%20them%20as%20complementary%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anton%20Severin%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20research%20at%20the%20Health%20and%20Fitness%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETen%20franchisees%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20acknowledged%20those%20broader%20challenges.%20They%20also%20blame%20Mayweather%20and%20company%20executives%20for%20the%20poor%20performance.%20They%20said%20they%20believed%20the%2048-year-old%20former%20prizefighter%2C%20with%20a%20social%20media%20following%20in%20the%20tens%20of%20millions%20and%20status%20as%20one%20of%20boxing's%20most%20recognizable%20champions%2C%20had%20the%20power%20to%20break%20through%2C%20much%20like%20George%20Foreman%20did%20with%20his%20famous%20electric