de%20any%20services%20whatsoever%20to%20franchisees%2C%20other%20than%20licensing%20his%20name.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Lee%2C%20an%20investor%20who%20purchased%20an%20equity%20stake%20in%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20the%20franchise%2C%20MW%20Fitness%20Holdings%2C%20had%20nothing%20but%20good%20things%20to%20say%20about%20the%20business.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20huge%20fan%20of%20Floyd%20and%20very%20happy%20to%20be%20an%20investor%20in%20Mayweather%20Fitness%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%20when%20reached%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220d8f117e-1acd-4e8f-b843-d78db7df598f%5C%22%3EBirth%20of%20a%20boxing%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMayweather%20Boxing%20and%20Fitness%20was%20the%20brainchild%20of%20James%20Williams%2C%20a%2045-year-old%2C%20British-born%20Wharton%20grad%20who%20previously%20worked%20as%20a%20corporate%20lawyer%20and%20as%20a%20business%20consultant%20for%20Bain%20%26amp%3B%20Company.%20He%20met%20Mayweather%20in%202013%20and%20said%20he%20was%20amazed%20that%20the%20fighter%2C%20then%20near%20the%20peak%20of%20his%20boxing%20career%2C%20was%20an%20untapped%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20had%20never%20taken%20a%20major%20licensing%2C%20sponsorship%2C%20or%20endorsement%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Williams%20as%20CEO%2C%20Mayweather%20Fitness%20and%20Boxing%20launched%20in%202017%2C%20the%20year%20Mayweather%20fought%20mixed%20martial%20arts%20star%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmayweather-mcgregor-fight-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EConor%20McGregor%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20one%20of%20boxing's%20most%20lucrative%20superfights.%20A%202023%20financial%20filing%20says%20Mayweather%20owns%2031.45%20percent%20of%20parent%20company%20MW%20Fitness%20Holdings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Floyd%20Mayweather%20punches%20Conor%20McGregor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68366896ca50259add4d247d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFloyd%20Mayweather%20punches%20Conor%20McGregor%20during%20their%202017%20fight.%3Cp%3EPA%20Images%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20chain%20has%20struggled%2C%20but%20attributed%20its%20difficulties%20to%20the%20problems%20in%20the%20broader%20fitness%20market.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20some%20franchisees%20may%20not%20have%20followed%20the%20playbook%20for%20success%20provided%20by%20him%20and%20his%20corporate%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFranchisees%20think%20Floyd%20is%20the%20silver%20bullet%20to%20a%20business%20that%20may%20be%20struggling%2C%20and%20he's%20just%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20going%20to%20make%20it%20successful%20is%20an%20engaged%20owner%20who's%20in%20there%2C%20who%20has%20a%20strong%20team%2C%20who's%20calling%20every%20day%2C%20training%20their%20team%20on%20scripts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20provided%20a%20screen%20recording%20of%20hundreds%20of%20publicity%20photos%20and%20videos%20of%20Mayweather%20taken%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20marketing%20the%20gyms%20and%20creating%20online%20and%20studio%20content.%20The%20pictures%20and%20videos%20depict%20Mayweather%20on%20a%20handful%20of%20occasions%2C%20including%20a%20visit%20to%20a%20gym%20in%20Torrance%2C%20California%2C%20and%20another%20location%20in%20Kansas%20City%2C%20Missouri%2C%20that%20was%20owned%20by%20Mayweather's%20brother-in-law.%20Both%20studios%20have%20since%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20also%20shared%20a%20video%20of%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20Instagram%20stories%20that%20Mayweather%20appears%20to%20have%20posted%20in%20a%20single%20batch%20in%20October%202022.%20(Knowing%20exactly%20what%20an%20Instagram%20user%20posts%20on%20the%20platform%20is%20difficult%20because%20stories%20disappear%20after%2024%20hours%20with%20no%20trace.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20deeply%20misleading%20to%20suggest%20there's%20a%20lack%20of%20promotion%20or%20contribution%20from%20Floyd%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20wrote%20in%20a%20follow-up%20email%20to%20BI.%20%26quot%3BFloyd%20is%20featured%20in%20every%20studio%2C%20every%20day%2C%20both%20in%20digital%20programming%20and%20marketing%20materials.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f550526-0553-485a-9fb2-0bee453528b5%5C%22%3EBetting%20on%20a%20champion%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%202023%20public%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F1999517%2F000199951723000005%2Fmwfid.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiling%3C%2Fa%3E%20described%20Mayweather%20as%20%26quot%3Bresponsible%20for%20supporting%20marketing%20and%20promotion%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGym%20owners%20contend%20that%20Mayweather%20showed%20a%20lack%20of%20involvement%20that%20was%20obvious%20and%2C%20in%20some%20instances%2C%20galling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20permanent%20post%20that%20Mayweather%20made%20on%20Instagram%20to%20his%20nearly%2030%20million%20followers%20about%20the%20brand%20was%20in%20October%202021.%20During%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxbusiness.com%2Fvideo%2F6369364020112%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappearance%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February%20on%20Fox%20News%2C%20he%20promoted%20a%20new%20line%20of%20supplements%20but%20didn't%20mention%20that%20they%20would%20be%20sold%20in%20his%20gyms.%20As%20a%20guest%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Tonight%20Show%20Starring%20Jimmy%20Fallon%26quot%3B%20the%20same%20day%2C%20Mayweather%20again%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Freload%3D9%26app%3Ddesktop%26v%3DuAd1_Z5wB70%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscussed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20supplements%2C%20a%20lavish%20weeklong%20birthday%20celebration%20in%20Miami%2C%20and%20his%20diamond-encrusted%20watch.%20He%20mentioned%20the%20gyms%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20offer%20from%20Mayweather%20to%20visit%20gyms%20that%20were%20in%20need%20of%20a%20boost%20of%20publicity%3F%20Several%20franchisees%20said%20they%20were%20rebuffed%20or%20told%20they%20would%20have%20to%20pay%20Mayweather%20around%20%2430%2C000%20to%20make%20an%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcSpedon%20said%20Mayweather%20personally%20told%20her%20after%20his%20speech%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20that%20he%20would%20visit%20one%20of%20her%20Chicago%20gyms.%20When%20she%20followed%20up%20in%20the%20months%20after%20the%20event%2C%20the%20corporate%20team%20ignored%20her%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20just%20gave%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDerek%20Love%2C%20who%20opened%20a%20Mayweather%20Boxing%20and%20Fitness%20location%20in%20Decatur%2C%20Georgia%2C%20in%20late%202022%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20grown%20daughter%2C%20said%20that%20he%2C%20too%2C%20was%20told%20Mayweather%20would%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20six%20months%20before%20his%20gym%20opened%2C%20Love%20met%20Mayweather%20at%20the%20grand%20opening%20of%20a%20location%20in%20Nashville%20that%20is%20part-owned%20by%20Mayweather's%20cousin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20money%20man%2C%20the%20money%20man%2C%20the%20money%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20Mayweather%20says%20in%20a%20video%20clip%20recorded%20by%20Love.%20%26quot%3BMayweather%20Boxing%20and%20Fitness%2C%20Decatur%2C%20Georgia%2C%20I'm%20on%20my%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELove%20said%20the%20corporate%20team%20later%20told%20him%20there%20would%20be%20a%20fee.%20When%20he%20learned%20from%20other%20gym%20owners%20that%20it%20was%20in%20the%20range%20of%20%2430%2C000%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bshocked%20and%20never%20asked%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20in%20April%202022%2C%20the%20company's%20federally%20mandated%20franchise%20disclosure%20document%20included%20a%20section%20that%20franchisees%20could%20request%20a%20visit%20from%20Mayweather%20for%20%2450%2C000.%20Earlier%20versions%20of%20the%20document%20made%20no%20mention%20of%20such%20a%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELove%2C%20a%2058-year-old%20retired%20military%20veteran%2C%20closed%20his%20gym%20in%20early%202024%20and%20said%20he%20and%20his%20family%20lost%20roughly%20a%20million%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FGjesgUQY5eA%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Floyd%20Mayweather%20and%20James%20Williams%2C%20CEO%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20said%20that%20Mayweather%20did%20visit%20some%20gyms%20and%20said%20that%20the%20company%20gathered%20data%20that%20showed%20the%20former%20champ's%20presence%20didn't%20boost%20membership.%20Gyms%20that%20did%20not%20receive%20an%20appearance%20had%202.6%20times%20more%20revenue%20and%20sold%207.4%20times%20as%20many%20memberships%20than%20those%20that%20did%2C%20Williams%20said%20in%20an%20email%20to%20BI.%20Williams%20did%20not%20provide%20any%20of%20the%20data%2C%20including%20which%20gyms%20were%20used%20to%20make%20those%20calculations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20showed%20up%2C%20it%20would%20be%20probably%20a%20three-hour%20high%20where%20people%20would%20gather%20%E2%80%94%20boxing%20enthusiasts%2C%20Floyd%20enthusiasts%20%E2%80%94%20not%20people%20that%20are%20paying%20%24150%20a%20month%20or%20%24160%20a%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kerry%20Hamilton-Gannaway%2C%20a%20franchisee%20who%20owns%20a%20gym%20in%20Melbourne%2C%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurrel%20Wilks%2C%20a%20friend%20of%20Mayweather's%20who%20co-founded%20the%20gym%20chain%20with%20Williams%20and%20Mayweather%2C%20said%20Mayweather%20didn't%20come%20to%20the%20studio%20he%20opened%20in%20Newport%20Coast%2C%20California%20and%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20ask%20him%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20ain't%20about%20Floyd%20showing%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Wilks%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20going%20to%20get%20the%20gym%20going%20is%20the%20hard%20work%20and%20dedication%20that%20we%20have%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilks'%20gym%20failed%20and%20closed%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuy%20Castillo%2C%20a%20commercial%20contractor%20in%20Orange%20County%2C%20California%2C%20who%20opened%20a%20Mayweather%20location%20in%20San%20Diego%20in%202022%2C%20bristled%20at%20the%20idea%20that%20a%20visit%20from%20Mayweather%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20impactful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would've%20had%20500-800%20members%20right%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Castillo%20said%2C%20speculating%20on%20the%20customer%20interest%20Mayweather%20could%20have%20generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECastillo%20said%20he%20launched%20his%20studio%20with%20about%20250%20initial%20members%20by%20resorting%20to%20heavy%20promotional%20discounts.%20He%20closed%20the%20gym%20at%20the%20end%20of%202023%2C%20he%20said%2C%20at%20a%20loss%20of%20nearly%20%242%20million%20%E2%80%94%20much%20of%20it%20from%20rent%20he%20had%20to%20pay%20after%20the%20business%20went%20dark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Boxer%20Floyd%20Mayweather%20stands%20to%20the%20right%20of%20franchise%20owner%20Guy%20Castillo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68366351c6ad288d148202d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGuy%20Castillo%2C%20owner%20of%20a%20Floyd%20Mayweather%20gym%20franchise%2C%20with%20the%20boxing%20champ%20at%20a%202021%20event%20in%20Las%20Vegas.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Guy%20Castillo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20franchisees%20said%20they%20suffered%20life-changing%20financial%20setbacks%20as%20a%20result%20of%20their%20investment%20in%20the%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESunny%20Dharni%20purchased%20the%20rights%20for%2010%20franchises%20in%20Northern%20California%20in%202019%20for%20%24120%2C000%20and%20opened%20two%20studios%2C%20in%20Elk%20Grove%20and%20Folsom%2C%20California%2C%20in%202021%20and%202023%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDharni%20was%20evicted%20from%20the%20Elk%20Grove%20studio%20in%202024%2C%20and%20his%20former%20landlord%20is%20suing%20for%20%2470%2C000%20in%20unpaid%20rent.%20He%20said%20he%20sold%20the%20Folsom%20location%20at%20a%20loss%20last%20year.%20In%20May%2C%20another%20creditor%20sued%20the%20limited%20liability%20company%20associated%20with%20Dharni's%20studios%20for%20%2475%2C000%2C%20alleging%20breach%20of%20contract%20and%20non-payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDharni%20said%20he%20has%20struggled%20to%20pay%20back%20roughly%20%24700%2C000%20in%20business%20loans%20he%20took%20out%20to%20help%20launch%20the%20studios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20terrible%2C%20I%20mean%20depressing%2C%20to%20say%20the%20least%2C%26quot%3B%20Dharni%2C%2031%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BLosing%20everything%20that%20I%20had%20saved%20up%20%E2%80%94%20my%20credit%20is%20shot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDharni%20said%20he%20tried%20to%20arrange%20a%20deal%20with%20Williams%20to%20sell%20some%20of%20his%20franchise%20rights%20back%20to%20the%20company%20to%20recoup%20a%20portion%20of%20his%20losses.%20Williams%2C%20he%20said%2C%20eventually%20stopped%20returning%20his%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20almost%20like%20a%20betrayal%20type%20of%20feeling%2C%26quot%3B%20Dharni%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cd1608d5-af10-4f6b-985d-99b2681a54cc%5C%22%3EMayweather%20vs.%20Franchisees%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWeis%20and%20Castillo%20are%20in%20a%20group%20of%20six%20gym%20owners%20who%20are%20working%20with%20an%20attorney%20and%20seeking%20to%20initiate%20mediation%20with%20the%20brand%20to%20reimburse%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20group%20of%20four%20franchisees%20sued%20the%20company%2C%20along%20with%20Mayweather%2C%20Williams%2C%20and%20Wilks%2C%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20Superior%20Court%20last%20year.%20The%20lawsuit%2C%20which%20is%20ongoing%2C%20claims%20that%20the%20plaintiffs%20%26quot%3Blost%20over%20%248%2C000%2C000%20due%20to%20defendants'%20misrepresentations%20and%20misleading%20statements%26quot%3B%20and%20seeks%20financial%20restitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suit%20alleges%20that%20Williams%20misled%20the%20franchisees%20on%20several%20occasions%20by%20telling%20them%20that%20the%20company%20would%20buy%20their%20locations%20if%20they%20struggled%20and%20that%20the%20business%20was%20growing%20rapidly%2C%20even%20as%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20it%20wasn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20also%20accuses%20the%20company's%20cofounders%20of%20taking%20%242%20million%20out%20of%20the%20business%20%26quot%3Bfor%20their%20own%20personal%20enrichment.%26quot%3B%20Mayweather%20Boxing%20and%20Fitness%20denied%20the%20allegations%20in%20an%20answer%20to%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20categorically%20reject%20their%20claims%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20wrote%20in%20an%20email.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20spurious%20and%20unfounded%2C%20and%20we%20are%20defending%20against%20them%20vigorously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222214%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Burrel%20Wilks%2C%20a%20business%20associate%20of%20Floyd%20Mayweather%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68366c3bc6ad288d14820319%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBurrel%20Wilks%20cofounded%20the%20chain%20of%20boxing%20gyms.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Bezjian%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20several%20franchisees%20have%20lost%20financially%2C%20Mayweather%20disclosed%20that%20he%20made%20%243%20million%20in%20royalties%20in%20a%20legal%20letter%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tmz.com%2F2025%2F05%2F20%2Ffloyd-mayweather-fitness-letter-lawsuit%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20reported%20by%20TMZ%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20his%20lawyer%20sent%20to%20Williams%2C%20Wilks%2C%20and%20the%20fitness%20company%20in%20May%20as%20part%20of%20a%20dispute%20over%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20business.%20(Williams%20said%20all%20payments%20to%20Mayweather%20came%20from%20MW%20Fitness%20Holdings%2C%20the%20parent%20company.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20was%20sent%20after%20Business%20Insider%20presented%20questions%20to%20Mayweather's%20lawyer%20about%20the%20complaints%20from%20gym%20franchisees%2C%20and%20it%20referenced%20BI's%20reporting%20while%20drawing%20distance%20between%20the%20boxer%20and%20the%20fitness%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Mayweather%20has%20not%20participated%20in%20management%2C%20operations%2C%20or%20strategic%20oversight%20of%20these%20entities%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20read.%20%26quot%3BDespite%20his%20limited%20involvement%20as%20a%20brand%20ambassador%2C%20your%20organizations%20have%20continually%20and%20improperly%20exploited%20his%20name%2C%20image%2C%20and%20likeness%20for%20financial%20gain%20while%20simultaneously%20embroiling%20him%20in%20lawsuits%20and%20negative%20press%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20told%20TMZ%3A%20%26quot%3BMy%20team%20and%20I%20have%20consistently%20operated%20Mayweather%20Fitness%20with%20integrity%20and%20in%20full%20compliance%20with%20all%20applicable%20laws%20and%20regulations%2C%20and%20we%20look%20forward%20to%20that%20being%20clearly%20reflected%20through%20current%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20always%20had%20a%20great%20relationship%20with%20Floyd%2C%20and%20want%20to%20make%20clear%20that%20the%20letter%20is%20correct%20in%20stating%20that%20I%20oversee%20and%20am%20responsible%20for%20all%20operational%20aspects%20of%20the%20business.%20Floyd%20is%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20day-to-day%20operations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20into%20a%20retail%20franchise%20is%20inherently%20risky%2C%20experts%20say.%20If%20the%20business%20begins%20to%20falter%2C%20franchisees%20have%20little%20leeway%20to%20adjust%20the%20product%20offering%2C%20design%20elements%2C%20or%20business%20model%20without%20corporate%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20fungible%20asset%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ben%20Lawrence%2C%20professor%20of%20franchise%20entrepreneurship%20at%20Georgia%20State%20University's%20J.%20Mack%20Robinson%20College%20of%20Business.%20%26quot%3BYou%20build%20to%20the%20specifications%20of%20the%20brand%2C%20and%20then%20you%20invest%20your%20life%20in%20that%20brand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMW%20Fitness%20Holdings%20disclosed%20its%20financial%20challenges%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F1999517%2F000199951723000005%2Fmwfid.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoffering%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20with%20the%20SEC%20ahead%20of%20a%202023%20equity%20crowdfunding%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBalance%20sheets%20showed%20net%20losses%20of%20%243.7%20million%20in%202021%20and%20%243.3%20million%20in%202022.%20Revenue%20declined%20by%20%242.2%20million%20in%202022%3B%20royalty%20payments%20from%20franchises%20doubled%2C%20while%20money%20from%20property%20and%20gym%20equipment%20sales%20to%20franchisees%2C%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20revenue%2C%20was%20down%20sharply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20filing%20showed%20the%20company%20had%20%242.4%20million%20of%20debt%20that%20was%20personally%20guaranteed%20by%20Williams%2C%20who%20also%20lent%20the%20company%20%24400%2C000%20at%20a%207%25%20interest%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20made%20a%20%24100%2C000%20loan%20to%20Mayweather%2C%20in%202017.%20That%20debt%20was%20not%20repaid%2C%20and%20the%20company%20wrote%20it%20off%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20red%20ink%2C%20Mayweather%20said%20the%20company%20was%20poised%20for%20%26quot%3Bexponential%26quot%3B%20growth%20in%20a%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frepublic.com%2Fmayweath