ns-apply%2Famp_articleshow%2F121560968.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fwhat-is-the-uae-golden-visa-can-indians-apply%2Famp_articleshow%2F121560968.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20data%20confirms%20it%3A%20AI%20is%20taking%20human%20jobs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Robot%20hand%20holding%20a%20coffee%20mug%20with%20a%20cubicle%20office%20in%20the%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683a10c36ffb6822ec61d692%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%C2%A0%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Ava%20Horton%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshopify-ceo-tobi-lutke-employees-prove-ai-job-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShopify%3C%2Fa%3E's%20CEO%20told%20his%20managers%20he%20was%20implementing%20a%20new%20rule%3A%20Before%20asking%20for%20more%20head%20count%2C%20they%20had%20to%20prove%20that%20AI%20couldn't%20do%20the%20job%20as%20well%20as%20a%20human%20would.%20A%20few%20weeks%20later%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-messaging-backlash-duolingo-shopify-controversy-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDuolingo%3C%2Fa%3E's%20CEO%20announced%20a%20similar%20decree%20and%20went%20even%20further%20%E2%80%94%20saying%20the%20company%20would%20gradually%20phase%20out%20contractors%20and%20replace%20them%20with%20AI.%20The%20announcements%20matched%20what%20I've%20been%20hearing%20in%20my%20own%20conversations%20with%20employers%3A%20Because%20of%20AI%2C%20they%20are%20hiring%20less%20than%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20started%20reporting%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-ai-technology-end-of-coding-software-developers-jobs-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT's%20impact%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20labor%20market%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20take%20many%20years%20for%20AI%20to%20meaningfully%20reshape%20the%20job%20landscape.%20But%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20I've%20found%20myself%20wondering%20if%20the%20AI%20revolution%20has%20already%20arrived.%20To%20answer%20that%20question%2C%20I%20asked%20Revelio%20Labs%2C%20an%20analytics%20provider%20that%20aggregates%20huge%20reams%20of%20workforce%20data%20from%20across%20the%20internet%2C%20to%20see%20if%20it%20could%20tell%20which%20jobs%20are%20already%20being%20replaced%20by%20AI.%20Not%20in%20some%20hypothetical%20future%2C%20but%20right%20now%20%E2%80%94%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZanele%20Munyikwa%2C%20an%20economist%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reveliolabs.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERevelio%20Labs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20started%20by%20looking%20at%20the%20job%20descriptions%20in%20online%20postings%20and%20identifying%20the%20listed%20responsibilities%20that%20AI%20can%20already%20perform%20or%20augment.%20She%20found%20that%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20the%20share%20of%20AI-doable%20tasks%20in%20online%20job%20postings%20has%20declined%20by%2019%25.%20After%20further%20analysis%2C%20she%20reached%20a%20startling%20conclusion%3A%20The%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20drop%20took%20place%20because%20companies%20are%20hiring%20fewer%20people%20in%20roles%20that%20AI%20can%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20Munyikwa%20segmented%20all%20the%20occupations%20into%20three%20buckets%3A%20those%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20AI-doable%20tasks%20(high-exposure%20roles)%2C%20those%20with%20relatively%20few%20AI-doable%20tasks%20(low-exposure%20roles)%2C%20and%20those%20in%20between.%20Since%20OpenAI%20released%20ChatGPT%20in%202022%2C%20she%20found%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20decline%20in%20job%20openings%20across%20the%20board.%20But%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-collar-recession-hiring-slump-jobs-tech-industry-applications-rejection-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiring%20downturn%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20steeper%20for%20high-exposure%20roles%20(31%25)%20than%20for%20low-exposure%20roles%20(25%25).%20In%20short%2C%20jobs%20that%20AI%20can%20perform%20are%20disappearing%20from%20job%20boards%20faster%20than%20those%20that%20AI%20can't%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FHj7QP%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FHj7QP%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWhich%20jobs%20have%20the%20most%20exposure%20to%20AI%3F%20Those%20that%20handle%20a%20lot%20of%20tech%20functions%3A%20database%20administrators%2C%20IT%20specialists%2C%20information%20security%2C%20and%20data%20engineers.%20The%20jobs%20with%20the%20lowest%20exposure%20to%20AI%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20are%20in-person%20roles%20like%20restaurant%20managers%2C%20foremen%2C%20and%20mechanics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20analysis%20to%20show%20the%20early%20impact%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-productivity-boost-job-performance-inequality-economics-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20on%20the%20labor%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%202023%2C%20a%20group%20of%20researchers%20at%20Washington%20University%20and%20New%20York%20University%20homed%20in%20on%20a%20set%20of%20professionals%20who%20are%20particularly%20vulnerable%3A%20freelancers%20in%20writing-related%20occupations.%20After%20the%20introduction%20of%20ChatGPT%2C%20the%20number%20of%20jobs%20in%20those%20fields%20dropped%20by%202%25%20on%20the%20freelancing%20platform%20Upwork%20%E2%80%94%20and%20monthly%20earnings%20declined%20by%205.2%25.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20short%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20researchers%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3Bgenerative%20AI%20reduces%20overall%20demand%20for%20knowledge%20workers%20of%20all%20types.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FhBcCr%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FhBcCr%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Revelio%20Labs%2C%20Munyikwa%20is%20careful%20about%20expanding%20on%20the%20implications%20of%20her%20own%20findings.%20It's%20unclear%2C%20she%20says%2C%20if%20AI%20in%20its%20current%20iteration%20is%20actually%20capable%20of%20doing%20all%20the%20white-collar%20work%20that%20employers%20think%20it%20can.%20It%20could%20be%20that%20CEOs%20at%20companies%20like%20Shopify%20and%20Duolingo%20will%20wake%20up%20one%20day%20and%20discover%20that%20hiring%20less%20for%20AI-exposed%20roles%20was%20a%20bad%20move.%20Will%20it%20affect%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20work%20or%20the%20creativity%20of%20employees%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20ultimately%2C%20the%20bottom%20line%3F%20The%20answer%20will%20determine%20how%20enduring%20the%20AI%20hiring%20standstill%20will%20prove%20to%20be%20in%20the%20years%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20companies%20already%20appear%20to%20be%20doing%20an%20about-face%20on%20their%20AI%20optimism.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20fintech%20company%20Klarna%20boasted%20that%20its%20investment%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%20had%20enabled%20it%20to%20put%20a%20freeze%20on%20human%20hiring.%20An%20AI%20assistant%2C%20it%20reported%2C%20was%20doing%20%26quot%3Bthe%20equivalent%20work%20of%20700%20full-time%20agents.%26quot%3B%20But%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20Klarna%20has%20changed%20its%20tune.%20It%20has%20started%20hiring%20human%20agents%20again%2C%20acknowledging%20that%20its%20AI-driven%20cost-cutting%20p