20the%20US%20government.%20The%20Department%20of%20Defense%20is%20its%20biggest%20customer%2C%20making%20up%2041%25%20of%20its%20fourth-quarter%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStartup%20founders%20need%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Btechnical%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20product%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20even%20%26quot%3Bethnographers%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdesigners%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tan%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewho%20worked%20at%20Palantir%20from%202005%20to%202007.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20want%20the%20person%20on%20the%20second%20meeting%20to%20see%20the%20demo%20you%20put%20together%20based%20on%20the%20stuff%20you%20heard%2C%20and%20you%20want%20them%20to%20say%2C%20'Wow%2C%20I've%20never%20seen%20anything%20like%20that.'%20And%20take%20my%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fd173e22-2935-4df6-860a-e2b0a4634677%5C%22%3EFounders%20closing%20'six%2C%20seven-figure%20deals'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20hands-on%20approach%20is%20already%20delivering%20big%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYC%20partner%20Diana%20Hu%20said%20she%20and%20her%20team%20have%20seen%20founders%20close%20%26quot%3Bsix%2C%20seven%20seven-figure%20deals%26quot%3B%20with%20large%20enterprises%20by%20being%20forward-deployed%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20she%20said%2C%20a%20pair%20of%20founders%20wins%20a%20deal%20by%20walking%20into%20a%20boardroom%2C%20gathering%20context%2C%20and%20coming%20back%20the%20next%20day%20with%20a%20tailored%20AI%20demo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20deal%20is%20closed%2C%20some%20of%20these%20founders%20go%20on-site%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20customer%20support%20teams%2C%20continuously%20fine-tuning%20the%20software%20or%20language%20model%20to%20improve%20performance%2C%20said%20YC%20partner%20Harj%20Taggar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETan%20said%20this%20model%20gives%20AI%20startups%20a%20chance%20to%20outmaneuver%20giants%20like%20Salesforce%2C%20Oracle%2C%20and%20Booz%20Allen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quo