d%20later%20launched%20ChooseFI%2C%20which%20has%20been%20downloaded%2070%20million%20times%20since%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFIRE%2C%20or%20Financial%20Independence%20Retire%20Early%2C%20is%20a%20cute%20acronym%2C%20and%20we%20used%20it%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20early%20days.%20But%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20whether%20you%20are%20working%20full%20time%2C%20part%20time%2C%20or%20are%20completely%20retired.%20It's%20all%20about%20financial%20independence%20%E2%80%94%20reaching%20a%20point%20where%20we%20can%20control%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-independence-retire-early-saving-loneliness-retreat-bali-making-friends-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eonly%20thing%20that%20matters%20in%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20our%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20countless%20questions%20I%20get%20from%20listeners%20or%20those%20who%20read%20our%20newsletter%2C%20there%20are%20four%20common%20mistakes%20I%20see%20early%20retirees%20make%20that%20keep%20them%20unsatisfied%20post-FI%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e8023d71-189e-474e-a7e9-07123dbdc90b%5C%22%3E1.%20They're%20retiring%20%3Cem%3Efrom%3C%2Fem%3E%20something%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20broad%20category%20of%20mistakes%20I%20see%20involves%20people%20simply%20not%20having%20ideas%20of%20what%20they%20want%20to%20do%20in%20their%20post-work%20life.%20In%20the%202013-2017%20timeframe%2C%20FI%20was%20about%20getting%20to%20a%20number%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%2C%20and%20little%20else%20mattered.%20It's%20getting%20better%2C%20but%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20mindset%20shift%20to%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20running%20away%20from%20a%20job%2C%20but%20I'm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fearly-retirement-advice-social-security-strategies-health-crisis-aging-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erunning%20toward%20a%20life%20that%20I%20want%20to%20live%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20were%20just%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%