ks)%20and%20wear%20them%20for%20family%20pictures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20already%20over%2080%2C%20which%20seems%20to%20mean%20you%20just%20never%20know%20if%20there%20will%20be%20a%20bad%20fall%20or%20serious%20health%20issues%20at%20any%20given%20moment.%20Basically%2C%20the%20time%20to%20go%20was%20yesterday%2C%20so%20after%20chatting%20with%20my%20younger%20siblings%2C%20we%20got%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b1adac36-5629-400b-ad8c-a31acd431f4c%5C%22%3EI'm%20grateful%20we%20made%20it%20happen%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyearly-multigenerational-family-trip-is-one-of-my-cherished-memories-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanning%20a%20multigenerational%20trip%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20involves%20five%20adults%20with%20their%20own%20schedules%20and%20three%20young%20kids%20to%20another%20country%20is%20no%20small%20feat%2C%20we%20managed%20to%20make%20it%20happen%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I'm%20forever%20grateful%20we%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20primary%20challenges%20was%20finding%20places%20to%20stay%20that%20allowed%20room%20for%20everyone%20and%20thanks%20to%20an%20amazing%20traditional%20Korean%20house%2C%20called%20a%20%3Cem%3Ehanok%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20my%20brother%20found%20on%20AirBnB%20and%20another%20spacious%20multi-room%20condo%20Airbnb%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20be%20together%20but%20still%20have%20some%20space%20to%20spread%20out%2C%20which%20I%20would%20argue%20is%20essential%20with%20a%20trip%20with%20multiple%20family%20members.%20I'll%20never%20forget%20meeting%20aunts%20and%20uncles%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20my%20kids%20will%20talk%20about%20all%20the%20things%20we%20did%20together%20with%20their%20grandfather%20and%20uncles%20and%20beg%20to%20go%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20trip%20was%20now%20over%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20but%20dad%20still%20raves%20about%20it.%20I%20made%20him%20a%20photo%20book%20to%20remember%20the%20trip%20and%20it%20wasn't%20all%20the%20sightseeing%20we%20did%20or%20delicious%20food%20we%20ate%20he%20remembers%2C%20it%20was%20just%20the%20time%20spent%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b44c43ad-b84f-4c37-b278-60b83f6cf7ff%5C%22%3EWe%20did%20the%20same%20for%20my%20husband's%20parents%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFast-forward%20a%20year%20later%20and%20we%20were%20able%20to%20make%20another%20parent's%20dream%20trip%20with%20their%20grandchildren%20come%20true.%20My%20mother-in-law%20is%20a%20lifelong%20equestrian%20and%20had%20often%20brought%20up%20wanting%20to%20take%20a%20trail%20ride%20with%20the%20entire%20family%20at%20a%20ranch.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20many%20of%20the%20grandkids%20were%20too%20young%20to%20ride%2C%20but%20this%20past%20year%20seemed%20like%20the%20perfect%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20headed%20off%20to%20the%20gorgeous%20Alisal%20Ranch%20in%20Santa%20Ynez%20for%20a%20memorable%20girls-only%20trip%2C%20from%20Grandma%20to%20the%20six-year-old.%20It%20was%20clearly%20a%20property%20meant%20for%20family%20reunions%20and%20multigenerational%20vacations.%20The%20cabin%20we%20stayed%20in%20had%20a%20clever%20Murphy%20bunk%20bed%2C%20couch%20bed%2C%20and%20spacious%20bedroom%20for%20Grandma%20to%20rest%20comfortably.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20slower%20pace%20of%20trip%20that%20appealed%20to%20both%20young%20and%20old.%20Sitting%20on%20the%20porch%20watching%20horses%20meandering%20around%20while%20the%20sunsets%20will%20always%20remain%20a%20highlight%2C%20as%20will%20the%20friendly%20goats%20in%20the%20barn%20the%20kids%20went%20back%20day%20after%20day%20to%20pet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEating%20each%20meal%20together%20and%20just%20hanging%20out%20is%20basically%20what%20any%20grandparent%20really%20wants%2C%20and%20we%20had%20that%20in%20spades.%20The%20trip%20culminated%20in%20a%20wonderful%20morning%20horse%20ride%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bcowboy%20breakfast%26quot%3B%20(the%20youngest%20and%20I%20went%20in%20a%20wagon%20instead).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20all-inclusive%20nature%20of%20the%20property%20made%20it%20a%20super%20easy%20no-fuss%20planning%20process%20and%20everyone%20got%20to%20do%20what%20they%20wanted%2C%20whether%20it%20was%20just%20running%20around%20the%20expansive%20lawn%2C%20making%20crafts%20in%20the%20kids'%20art%20room%2C%20or%20playing%20ping-pong%20and%20roasting%20s'mores%20with%20Grandma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20like%20me%20and%20have%20been%20sitting%20around%20wondering%20when%20to%20make%20a%20special%20trip%20with%20the%20grandparents%20happen%2C%20the%20answer%20is%20now.%20None%20of%20us%20are%20getting%20any%20younger%2C%20and%20it's%20such%20a%20precious%20window%20when%20everyone%20is%20healthy%20enough%2C%20the%20kids%20are%20willing%20and%20able%2C%20and%20you%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20make%20literal%20dreams%20come%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20never%20be%20a%20perfect%20time%20when%20work%20or%20extracurricular%20activities%20don't%20have%20to%20get%20rearranged%20but%20trust%20me%2C%20it's%20not%20something%20you'll%20ever%20regret.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftook-our-parents-on-bucket-list-multigenerational-trips-worth-it-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748807402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68069fdf3fe8d3928363a256%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftook-our-parents-on-bucket-list-multigenerational-trips-worth-it-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Our%20youngest%20child%20is%206%20and%20our%20parents%20are%20in%20their%2080s.%20We%20are%20all%20getting%20older%20and%20I%20realized%20the%20time%20to%20make%20this%20trip%20happen%20was%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(%20Esther%20Carlstone)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A112%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftook-our-parents-on-bucket-list-multigenerational-trips-worth-i