ble%20along%20the%20water%E2%80%99s%20edge.%20Saji%20begins%20with%20gentle%20stretches%20and%20simple%20exercises%2C%20weaving%20in%20warmth%20and%20joy%20with%20stories%20and%20playful%20games.%20He%20turns%20safety%20drills%20into%20moments%20of%20fun%2C%20asking%20children%20if%20they%20know%20how%20to%20find%20their%20way%20home%2C%20encouraging%20impromptu%20performances%2C%20filling%20the%20air%20with%20laughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20sun%20rises%2C%20it%20casts%20its%20glow%20on%20a%20riverbank%20filled%20with%20smiling%2C%20spirited%20faces%2C%20ready%20to%20greet%20the%20water.%20When%20asked%20what%20keeps%20people%20coming%20back%2C%20Saji%20simply%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20go%20to%20places%20where%20they%20find%20happiness.%20Then%20swimming%20just%20becomes%20an%20added%20benefit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Leila%20Badyari%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20pictures%20courtesy%20Valassery%20Swimming%20Club%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748595328000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D441515%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Every%20morning%20at%205%3A30%20AM%2C%20a%20quiet%20revolution%20unfolds%20on%20a%20Kerala%20riverbank.%20Led%20by%20one%20man%2C%20Saji%20Valuvassery%2C%20this%20floating%20classroom%20has%20taught%20over%2010%2C000%20people%20to%20swim%E2%80%94for%20free.%20More%20than%20a%20skill%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20lifeline%2C%20a%20community%2C%20and%20a%20powerful%20reminder%20that%20courage%20can%20be%20contagious.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hanna%20Paul%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F441515%2Fkeralas-valasseril-river-swimming-club-turning-tragedy-to-hope%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Engineer%20Leaves%20Tech%20Career%20To%20Save%20Endangered%20Indians%