9CWhat%20is%20waste%20for%20you%20becomes%20raw%20material%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yuvraj%20shares%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDesign%20meets%20durability%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20sustainability%20pivot%2C%20Yuvraj%20never%20compromised%20on%20design%20or%20quality.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20core%20cannot%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20insists%2C%20since%20he%20has%20a%20background%20in%20design%20and%20architecture.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20have%20built%20something%20that%20has%20to%20be%20in%20the%20sun%20for%2010%20to%2012%20years%2C%20it%20cannot%20fade%3B%20it%20needs%20to%20sustain.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESereno%E2%80%99s%20products%20are%20now%20designed%20to%20last%20over%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F243566%2Feconiture-ecofriendly-recycled-plastic-furniture-home-decor-friends-earn-crores-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2020%20years%20and%20are%20100%25%20recyclable%3C%2Fa%3E.%20From%20planters%20that%20hold%20large%20trees%20to%20stylish%20outdoor%20furniture%2C%20each%20item%20undergoes%20rigorous%20R%20and%20D%20and%20weather-resistance%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20speak%20for%20themselves.%20Sereno%E2%80%99s%20pieces%20now%20adorn%20five-star%20hotels%20and%20luxury%20properties%20around%20the%20world.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20today%2C%20Sereno%20is%20known%20for%20its%20beautiful%20design%2C%20and%20when%20we%20find%20people%20copying%20our%20designs%2C%20we%20know%20that%20we%20are%20doing%20something%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Yuvraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3