thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-27_11zon-1748439573.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-27_11zon-1748439573-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-27_11zon-1748439573-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-27_11zon-1748439573-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-27_11zon-1748439573-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-440604%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdailey%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20a%20powerful%20awareness%20campaign%20launched%20by%20Unipads%20to%20challenge%20menstrual%20taboos%20in%20rural%20areas.%20Picture%20source%3A%20vml.com%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeeta%E2%80%99s%20startup%20turned%20that%20exclusion%20into%20protest.%20In%20a%20bold%20and%20unforgettable%20act%2C%20these%20very%20women%2C%20those%20once%20shut%20out%20of%20kitchens%2C%20cooked%20and%20served%20a%20full-course%20meal%20at%20a%20fine-dining%20restaurant%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20Celebrities%2C%20influencers%2C%20and%20community%20leaders%20came%20not%20just%20to%20eat%2C%20but%20to%20witness%20a%20statement.%20The%20event%2C%20captured%20in%20a%20powerful%20documentary%2C%20went%20on%20to%20win%20a%20Silver%20Glass%20Lion%20at%20the%20Cannes%20Creativity%20Festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20latest%20effort%2C%20%E2%80%98School%20Miles%E2%80%99%2C%20carries%20the%20same%20spirit%20%E2%80%94%20challenging%20silence%20with%20action.%20Aimed%20at%20improving%20school%20attendance%20among%20adolescent%20girls%20during%20their%20periods%2C%20the%20initiative%20was%20piloted%20with%201%2C000%20girls%20across%20two%20states%20%E2%80%94%20Gujarat%20and%20Rajasthan.%20Each%20girl%20re